    "zh": "品牌级 Granger 仅 4%~15% 车系显著；把月度情感塞回销量模型后体积加权误差反而略升——舆情是销量的「同期/滞后指标」而非「先行指标」，故不能作预测特征。",
    "en": "Brand-level Granger is significant for only 4-15% of series; adding monthly sentiment to the sales model slightly raises volume-weighted error — sentiment is a coincident/lagging indicator, not a leading one, so it cannot be used as a predictive feature."
